Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,————————————————————- ＯＰ————————————————————\N- 　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:08.64,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てしない空をゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:12.03,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見えない翼が導く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:14.05,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥か彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:20.79,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}僕らを待つ　まだ見ぬ未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:30.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always　覚め切ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:33.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速すぎるthat night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:40.19,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明な闇に囲まれ　誰も似た輪の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:43.26,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you　あの日の風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:46.59,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺れ動いた場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:47.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:52.87,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全て君に合うためのプロセスだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:55.96,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:58.39,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:02.33,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方から聞こえる予感に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:06.43,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓動を震わせていたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.22,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:13.70,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:17.10,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光の中 目覚めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:20.76,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じてくれた君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:21.96,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:26.58,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここで生まれ変わる景色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:30.16,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷さえ今　誇りになる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:34.77,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}だから君とBurst The Gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:08.64,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有尽头的天空中行走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:12.03,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由看不见的羽翼引导
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:14.05,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向遥远的比方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:20.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}那看不见的未来依旧在等待我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:30.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always 不愿清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:33.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了 that night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:40.19,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那透明的黑暗包围 谁也逃不出这个圈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:43.26,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you 那日的风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:46.59,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变幻不定的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:47.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:52.87,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是为了与你相会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:55.96,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:58.39,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:02.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自彼方听闻的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:06.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我震动鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.22,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:13.70,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:17.10,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光的沐浴下 我渐渐清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:20.76,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:21.96,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:26.58,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里不断变化的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:30.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的伤口 是我的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:34.77,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}因为你和Burst The Gravity
